node.text: ✨Giveaway And New Aura Announcement!!✨ Thank you all so much for participating in my giveaway to guess my newest Aura color!! Say Hello to Ember!! It’s a mix of red, orange and pink. As well as my new Scrying Nebula Aura Crystals!! To show a side by side comparison of Ember, the last video features Sunset, Sunrise and Ember.☀️So if you voted blue, orange, pink or red your name will be entered into the giveaway and I will be choosing a winner tonight!!✨ Thank you all again for the love and support have a blessed day !!💕

node.text: Spending the day working on these beautiful crystal moon bell suncatchers!!✨🌿 Featuring a center crystal moon that varies from amethyst to agate druzy. With a top and bottom layer of rainbow prism crystals!! I’ll also have a different version available with a brass moon center!!✨Thank you all again for your love and support. I hope you’re enjoying all the previews of what’ll be available at my next restock!! Blessed day everyone!! #reels reels #suncatcher #suncatchers #crystalmoon #amethyst #instagram Instagram #rainbow

node.text: So excited to reveal these mini crystal incense holder sun catchers I finished this weekend!!✨🌸 Featuring a brass incense holder, crystal point top and 3 crystal sun catcher prisms. Each order will include 3 free incense cones of my favorite incense. As well as 3 to 6 polished stones!! Ranging from rose quartz, grey moonstone, rainbow obsidian and clear quartz!!✨🌿Thank you all again for commenting on my recent posts regarding the issue with Instagram. I appreciate all your love and support!!🌸Have a blessed day everyone!

node.text: Is it true Instagram will no longer be a photo sharing app??!!😵I’ve noticed a massive drop in views on my photos recently and after posting about it this week the top comment was instagrams newest update. So I did some research and found that although the app will still allow photos to be shared, it’s main goal is to be more like TikTok. Focusing more on promoting reels and videos. I honestly wish Instagram would stop changing everything about this app and give us back the chronological feed💔Thank you all again for commenting on my recent post and dm’ing me about this issue. Have a blessed day everyone !!!🌸✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sacra Luna® on July 05, 2021. May be an image of jewelry.

node.text: Not sure why Instagram is hiding all my new posts!!😭😭 I wanted to share the new sun catchers I’ve been working on but for some reason I’m not reaching anyone. Please let me know if you’re seeing my posts🌸😓✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sacra Luna® on July 05, 2021.

node.text: So excited to show some sneak peeks of what I’ve been working on!!✨🌸 New home decor, sun catcher jewelry and 3 new aura colors!!✨I’ll be announcing my restock date soon, just waiting on more supplies to arrive. Have a blessed day everyone!!🌿✨ Photo via Pinterest

Spending the morning organizing a new shipment of crystals that just arrived!!✨I’ve been so inspired by these druzy shapes especially the clouds and stars! So excited to work on a few today, I’ll post the progress in my stories!✨🌸🌿Have a blessed day everyone!!💕

node.text: So in love with how this beautiful crystal sun catcher wind chime turned out!!✨💕I tried posting it a few times to my stories but the bells kept getting muffled. Hopefully the sound will be clear on my reels✨I’ve been wanting to make wind chimes for a while but wasn’t sure how to incorporate them into my designs. At first I was only going to feature them with plant sun catchers but I really enjoy how they look with crystals too. What do you think !!??😍🌸 oh and I just realized there’s another new design in this video!! My crystal moon sun catcher garland!! I’ll do a video reveal for that beauty as well✨🌿 Thank you all again for your love and support! Have a blessed day! #reels #rainbow #suncatcher #suncatchers

node.text: Spending the day shipping out more cauldron sun catcher pre orders!!✨💕Thank you all so much for your patience and understanding!! These took a bit longer to make so I’m including a ton of extra crystals in everyone package💕 I also wanted to answer a few questions I’ve been getting regarding pre orders. Pre orders are available on my site during the day of my restock in my shop new items section. All restocks take place at 7pm eastern time. I usually have a variety of pre orders available ranging from cauldrons, incense holders and crystal sun catchers. The title of these listings always starts with “pre order”✨If you have anymore questions please let me know ! Blessed day everyone 🌸 photo via Pinterest
